item.description:
Soup, sandwiches and dessert - if you have any other preferences on the menu, email me thru the group as I'll be talking with the owner about a menu for us. Some of you who have been to this before may have some suggestions?

We will have reservations and our hosts are planning a menu just for us, so please change your reservation if you find you can't make it -- and please let us or the Inn (978.356.2431) know if you can't make it at the last minute.
